      "title": "Cheese Press",
      "pageid": 2090,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Cheese Press</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Cheese_Press.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cheese Press.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/79/Cheese_Press.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Turns milk into cheese.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><i>Cannot be sold</i>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Crafting</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Recipe Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Farming Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Farming\" title=\"Farming\">Farming</a>&#160;(Level 6)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Ingredients</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(45)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(45)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Hardwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/24px-Hardwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/36px-Hardwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Hardwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a>&#160;(10)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Copper Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/24px-Copper_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/36px-Copper_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Copper_Bar\" title=\"Copper Bar\">Copper Bar</a>&#160;(1)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Cheese Press</b> is a type of <a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan Equipment</a> used to make <a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>. It takes <a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> and turns it into <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a>. \n</p><p>Regular quality <a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> produces regular quality <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a>, and regular quality <a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> produces regular quality <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>. <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a> and <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a> produce gold quality cheeses. Cheese and Goat Cheese can be aged in <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Casks</a> to increase their value.\n</p><p>A Cheese Press is the reward for completing the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Red.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3f/Bundle_Red.png/24px-Bundle_Red.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3f/Bundle_Red.png/36px-Bundle_Red.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/3f/Bundle_Red.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Animal_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">Animal Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Bundles\">Pantry</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Products\">Products</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Cheese_Press&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Products\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/Animal_Products_Profitability\" title=\"Animal Products Profitability\">Animal Products Profitability</a></i></dd></dl>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Ingredients\n</th>\n<th>Processing Time<sup id=\"cite_ref-processtime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-processtime-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th>\n<th>Energy / Health\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Cheese.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cheese.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/a5/Cheese.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's your basic cheese.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a>&#160;(1)</span> <i>or</i><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 200m (&#8776;3h)</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Cheese.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a5/Cheese.png/24px-Cheese.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a5/Cheese.png/36px-Cheese.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a5/Cheese.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>230g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Cheese.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a5/Cheese.png/24px-Cheese.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a5/Cheese.png/36px-Cheese.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a5/Cheese.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>345g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-de