ge_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 200m (&#8776;3h)</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Cheese.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png/24px-Goat_Cheese.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png/36px-Goat_Cheese.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>400g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Cheese.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png/24px-Goat_Cheese.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png/36px-Goat_Cheese.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c8/Goat_Cheese.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>600g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 20px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/20px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/30px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/40px-Energy.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td style=\"vertical-align: bottom; padding-right: 6px;\">125</td>\n\t\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 20px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/20px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/30px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/40px-Health.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: bottom;\">56</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 20px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/20px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/30px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/40px-Ene