      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Cheese Press\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = {{Name|Farming Skill Icon|link=Farming|Level 6}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|45}}{{Name|Stone|45}}{{Name|Hardwood|10}}{{Name|Copper Bar|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Cheese Press''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] used to make [[Artisan Goods]]. It takes [[Milk]] and turns it into [[Cheese]]. \n\nRegular quality [[Milk]] produces regular quality [[Cheese]], and regular quality [[Goat Milk]] produces regular quality [[Goat Cheese]]. [[Large Milk]] and [[Large Goat Milk]] produce gold quality cheeses. Cheese and Goat Cheese can be aged in [[Cask]]s to increase their value.\n\nA Cheese Press is the reward for completing the {{Bundle|Animal||y}}.\n\n==Products==\n:''See also: [[Animal Products Profitability]]''\n<section begin=\"cheesepressproducts\"/>\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredients\n!Processing Time<noinclude><ref name=\"processtime\"/></noinclude>\n!Sell Price\n!Energy / Health\n|-\n|[[File:Cheese.png]]\n|[[Cheese]]\n|{{Description|Cheese}}\n|{{Name|Milk|1|class=inline}} ''or''{{Name|Large Milk|1}}\n|{{Duration|200m (&#8776;3h)}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Cheese|230|hide=silver,iridium|dsv=false}}\n|{{EdibilityGrid|Cheese|50|hide=silver,iridium|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Goat Cheese.png]]\n|[[Goat Cheese]]\n|{{Description|Goat Cheese}}\n|{{Name|Goat Milk|1|class=inline}} ''or''{{Name|Large Goat Milk|1}}\n|{{Duration|200m (&#8776;3h)}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Goat Cheese|400|hide=silver,iridium|dsv=false}}\n|{{EdibilityGrid|Goat Cheese|50|hide=silver,iridium|dsv=false}}\n|}<section end=\"cheesepressproducts\"/>\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Increased cheese sell price from {{Price|200}} to {{Price|230}}, goat cheese sell price from {{Price|375}} to {{Price|400}}. Cheese Presses can now be stacked in a player's [[inventory]] and in [[Chest|chests]].}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Käsepresse]]\n[[es:Prensa de queso]]\n[[fr:Presse à fromage]]\n[[it:Pressa per formaggi]]\n[[ja:チーズプレス]]\n[[ko:치즈 착제기]]\n[[hu:Sajtprés]]\n[[pt:Prensa de queijo]]\n[[ru:Пресс для сыра]]\n[[tr:Peynir Ezeceği]]\n[[zh:压酪机]]"
